  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Conjuration sphere (Natural Aspect (form) (fast healing option)), caster level 10th.</p>\n<p>Your companion&#8217;s fast healing becomes regeneration instead. Your companion is not dismissed if reduced to or below 0 hit points, nor are effects that trigger when the companion is reduced to 0 hit points (such as Explosive Companion) triggered, unless this regeneration is suppressed.</p>\n<p>This regeneration is overcome by two of the following damage types of your choice: acid, bludgeoning, cold, electricity, fire, negative energy, piercing, positive energy, or slashing. You cannot select a damage type that your companion possesses resistance or immunity to from a permanent ability, such as a (form) or (type) talent.</p>\n<p>Should your companion later gain resistance or immunity to the selected damage type from a permanent ability, you must select a new damage type.</p>\n",
